                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7918" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0105</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3530 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">让山村农户种地有搞头：西山坪村的实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Promoting Farming: Practice of Xishanping Village</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王容宽，王艺霖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆市北碚区东阳街道西山坪村村民委员会</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农地撂荒；农业机械化；新品种推广；产业拓展；山地农业；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Agricultural Land Abandonment; Agricultural Mechanisation; New Varieties Promotion; Industry Extension; Mountain Agriculture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">由于村民年纪大、山地自然条件限制、种地收益单一等原因，西山坪村面临农户不愿意耕种的困境，村委会为了让农户更加积极地耕种而采取了三大举措。其一，推动农业机械化；其二，推广新品种；其三，拓展村中产业。本案例适用于《农业经济管理》等课程中与“农村发展”或“乡村振兴”相关的章节。通过本案例教学，学员将掌握以下几方面知识：其一，山村农业发展的困境；其二，提升山地农业生产效率的举措；其三，增加山地农户收益的途径。西山坪村的实践经验也能启发广大基层管理者更好地应对农地撂荒问题以及促进当地农业农村农民的发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Due to the villagers’ incompetency to plant, natural constraints of the mountainous areas, and low income from farming, farmers in Xishanping Village feel farming not promising. The Committee has taken three major initiatives to make farmers more active in farming. Firstly, promote agricultural mechanisation; secondly, promote new varieties; and thirdly, extend the village&#39;s industries. This case is applicable to the chapters on &quot;rural development&quot; or &quot;rural revitalisation&quot; in the course &quot;Agricultural Economic Management&quot;. Through this case study, participants will acquire knowledge on the following aspects: firstly, the difficulties of agricultural development in mountainous areas; secondly, measures to improve the efficiency of agricultural production in mountainous areas; and thirdly, ways to increase the income of farmers in mountainous areas. The practical experience of Xishanping Village can also inspire village-level officials to better deal with agricultural land abandonment and promote agriculture in mountain villages.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《农业经济管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农地撂荒成因；农业机械化；新品种推广；乡村产业发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
